Dear Turo Hosts and Guests,

I hope this message finds you well. My name is Larry, and I am excited about the prospect of connecting with fellow Turo enthusiasts like yourself. As someone who values responsible and trustworthy interactions, I believe it's essential for both hosts and guests to feel confident in their Turo experiences.

About Me: 

I am an Accountant with a passion for Private Equity. Having traveled to 41 countries and counting, I've developed a deep appreciation for exploring new cultures and meeting diverse people. My commitment to responsibility and respect extends beyond my daily life to ensure a seamless and enjoyable experience for everyone involved.

Travel Experiences: 

Some of my favorite travel memories include traveling with my family, barbequing and sharing stories and thrill seeking exploring on extreme trips. These adventures have not only broadened my perspective but have also taught me the importance of open communication and mutual understanding.

Hobbies:

 In my free time, you'll find me going to the gym several days out the week and riding my ATV on the weekends. Whether it's the gym or ATVing, I believe in finding joy in life's simple pleasures and sharing those moments with others.

Dream Car: 

Ever since I was 12, I've dreamt of 67’ SS Chevy Chevelle. It's not just a mode of transportation for me; it represents a great“kick-up” fastback design. I am genuinely excited about the opportunity to experience it through Turo.

Driving Experience:

 With 20 years of driving experience, I prioritize safety and reliability on the road. I have a [Clean Driving Record/Provide any relevant certifications] and am committed to treating your vehicle with the utmost care and respect.

Get to Know Me Better:

 If you're interested in learning more about me, feel free to check out my profiles on www.linkedin.com/in/larryexantus/. These platforms provide a glimpse into my professional background and personal interests.
I understand the importance of trust and transparency in the Turo community, and I am more than happy to answer any questions you may have or provide additional information to ensure a positive experience for both parties. I look forward to the possibility of connecting and sharing fantastic Turo experiences together.

Best regards,

Larry Jay

I’m a grad student passionate about finance and economics, with a strong background in customer service. As a Turo host for 4 years, I’ve combined my love for cars with a commitment to providing great experiences. Looking forward to making your trip smooth and enjoyable! 🚗🙌🏽☀️🌊

Welcome to Sayvis LLC, your premier car sharing service in the beautiful city of West Palm Beach, Florida! We are dedicated to providing convenient, affordable, and eco-friendly transportation solutions for residents and visitors alike.

We believe in the power of community and sustainability. Our fleet of well-maintained vehicles includes a variety of options to suit your needs, whether you're running errands around town, exploring the vibrant streets of downtown West Palm Beach, or heading to the beach for a day of sun and relaxation.

With Turos easy-to-use mobile app, you can quickly locate and reserve a car near you, and hit the road in no time. Say goodbye to the hassles of traditional car ownership and experience the freedom of car sharing.

Whether you're a local looking for a convenient way to get around or a visitor eager to explore all that our city has to offer, Sayvis LLC rentals is here to help you make the most of your journey.

Scroll down to see our fleet, check available dates for your trip, and read reviews from past guests. We look forward to giving you an exceptional car rental experience!

Hello from A&J's Right Turn! 👋🏾

We’re AJ (Ashley and Joshua) Pean. A Florida-native, brother-sister duo working in the car rental space. 

We take a lot of pride in the work that we do and being able to provide a good experience for all of our renters. So let’s make your trip to Florida the best one yet!

We are a small family of three includes my husband and little boy, 15 months of age. We have been in South Florida for over 20 years and call Wellington/Royal Palm Beach our home.
We are pursuing Turo full time with multiple brand new cars to provide excellent customer service to our guests and expect them to treat our vehicles as their own.
We would try to accommodate our guests as much as possible.
Hope you enjoy your trip and our hospitality.
Thank you
Sidra & Family
